name: ARBEIT MACHT FREI
description:
So this guy says that his great group of guys don't need to wear face masks in their place of work, because they all work extremely hard together. Maybe, he continues, if the group of guys in the opposing corner were to work harder, they wouldn't need to wear face masks. Work will, literally, set you free.

Don't know why he's chosen to wear the badge in German, though. He *is* incredibly pretentious.
